com.estimote.coresdk.observation.region.mirror

Class MirrorRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.coresdk.observation.region.mirror.MirrorRegion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, Region

    public class MirrorRegion
extends java.lang.Object
implements Region, android.os.Parcelable
    Mirror region defines zone for mirror devices. Each region might consist of 1-N devices specified via list of deviceId in constructor. This list may be null - if so, any mirror device will match this region.
    Author:
    Pawel Dylag (pawel.dylag@estimote.com)
